flowchart LR
    Browser[React Frontend] --> Worker[Worker API<br/>Express + services]
    Worker --> AI[AI Providers<br/>Gemini/model gateway]
    Worker --> Registry[Unified Node Registry<br/>Schemas, credentials, field contracts]
    Worker --> Runtime[Execution Engine<br/>Dynamic node executor]
    Worker --> RDS[(AWS RDB/RDS<br/>PostgreSQL-compatible persistence)]
    Runtime --> Vault[Credential Vault / Resolver]
    Runtime --> External[External Apps and APIs<br/>Google, Gmail, Slack, HTTP, DBs, AI tools]
    Runtime --> Audit[Logs, checkpoints, runtime input audit]
